### Variabel baseUrl untuk mempermudah penggantian URL jika diperlukan
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api

### ==========================================
### QUIZ ENDPOINTS
### ==========================================

### 1. GET ALL QUIZZES
GET {{baseUrl}}/quizzes

###

### 2. GET ONE QUIZ
# Mengambil quiz beserta daftar pertanyaan di dalamnya
GET {{baseUrl}}/quizzes/1

###

### 3. CREATE QUIZ
POST {{baseUrl}}/quizzes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Kuis Sejarah Indonesia",
  "category": "Sejarah"
}

###

### 4. UPDATE QUIZ
PUT {{baseUrl}}/quizzes/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Kuis Sejarah Nasional Indonesia",
  "category": "Sejarah Umum"
}

###

### 5. DELETE QUIZ
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/quizzes/1

### ==========================================
### QUESTION ENDPOINTS
### ==========================================

### 1. GET ALL QUESTIONS
GET {{baseUrl}}/questions

###

### 2. GET ONE QUESTION
GET {{baseUrl}}/questions/1

###

### 3. CREATE QUESTION (Max 10 per Quiz)
# Pastikan quiz_id merujuk pada Quiz yang sudah ada di database
POST {{baseUrl}}/questions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quiz_id": 1,
  "question": "Siapakah presiden pertama Indonesia?",
  "options": [
    "Soekarno",
    "Soeharto",
    "B.J. Habibie",
    "Abdurrahman Wahid"
  ],
  "answer": 0
}

###

### 4. CREATE QUESTION KEDUA
POST {{baseUrl}}/questions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quiz_id": 1,
  "question": "Kapan hari kemerdekaan Indonesia?",
  "options": [
    "17 Agustus 1944",
    "17 Agustus 1945",
    "17 Agustus 1946",
    "17 Agustus 1947"
  ],
  "answer": 1
}

###

### 5. UPDATE QUESTION
PUT {{baseUrl}}/questions/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quiz_id": 1,
  "question": "Siapakah bapak proklamator dan presiden pertama Indonesia?",
  "options": [
    "Ir. Soekarno",
    "Soeharto",
    "B.J. Habibie",
    "Abdurrahman Wahid"
  ],
  "answer": 0
}

###

### 6. DELETE QUESTION
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/questions/1
